result.title: Interesting travelling blog
result.content:
Hi,

I would like to use the opportunity to advertise interesting travelling blog. My wife has just started it and she needs Facebook likes to make it more popular.

The idea is very interesting — how to organize exciting trips/road trips with a small baby (our 3 year old son :) ). Unfortunately it is currently in polish only. But at least if you liked the pictures (she puts a lot of effort to make each one looking nice), we would be extremely grateful for a Facebook like.

The blog: https://mousetheadventurer.com/

FB fan page: https://www.facebook.com/mousetheadventurer

Remember — each like makes our son smile. And karma returns :)

Thanks in advance!

Przemek
